'''''Blade of Sacrifice''''' was a [[Yuuzhan Vong]] [[Warship/Legends|warship]]. Following the [[Battle of Coruscant (Yuuzhan Vong War)|fall of Coruscant]], ''Blade of Sacrifice'' was recalled to [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] to join the massing Yuuzhan Vong fleet preparing to assault the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] force at [[Dac/Legends|Mon Calamari]].

